### Process Chat - Simple Example
POST http://localhost:5002/agent/process
Content-Type: application/json

[
  {
    "role": "user",
    "content": "I want to set up automatic bidding for auction #5. Maximum 50000, and always increase by 500. Check every hour."
  }
]

### Process Chat - Full Conversation
POST http://localhost:5002/agent/process
Content-Type: application/json

[
  {
    "role": "user",
    "content": "Hi! I need help setting up automatic bidding."
  },
  {
    "role": "assistant",
    "content": "Sure, I'd be happy to help! Which auction would you like to automate?"
  },
  {
    "role": "user",
    "content": "Auction #12."
  },
  {
    "role": "assistant",
    "content": "Okay. What's the maximum amount you want to bid?"
  },
  {
    "role": "user",
    "content": "Maximum 100000. Always increase by 1000, and check every 30 minutes."
  }
]

### Process Chat - Complex with Conditions
POST http://localhost:5002/agent/process
Content-Type: application/json

[
  {
    "role": "user",
    "content": "I'd like to set up autobid for auction #7. Max 75000, in steps of 750, every 2 hours. But only bid if there are more than 3 days remaining."
  }
]

### Process Chat - With Advanced Conditions
POST http://localhost:5002/agent/process
Content-Type: application/json

[
  {
    "role": "user",
    "content": "I want automatic bidding for auction #15. Maximum 200000. Initially increase by 1000, but above 50000 increase by 5000. If outbid, wait 30 seconds then bid again. Be more aggressive in the last 2 minutes. And avoid round numbers to be unpredictable."
  }
]

### Confirm Configuration
POST http://localhost:5002/agent/confirm
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": 0,
  "auctionId": 15,
  "userId": 0,
  "maxBidAmount": 200000,
  "incrementAmount": 1000,
  "intervalMinutes": 30,
  "isActive": true,
  "conditionsJson": {
    "increment_step_after": {
      "50000": 5000
    },
    "if_outbid": true,
    "react_delay_seconds": 30,
    "near_end_minutes": 2,
    "last_minute_rush": true,
    "avoid_round_numbers": true
  }
}
